{
  "_comment": "搜番发布页多跳适配草案。当前发布页链路可静态解析：sefan.vip 解出 ok.sofan.in，ok.sofan.in 再暴露 host2=to.sofan1.cc。实际搜索结果仍在 to.sofan1.cc 的 iframe 后端中，当前 JSON 插件协议不做 iframe 拼接和 JS 渲染，因此此文件先作为发布页多跳协议测试样例，不建议直接作为可用搜索源安装。",
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "sefan",
  "name": "搜番",
  "enabled": true,
  "baseUrl": "",
  "announcement": {
    "enabled": true,
    "steps": [
      {
        "url": "https://sefan.vip/",
        "urlPattern": "var\\s+spans='([^']+)'",
        "urlDecoding": "base64",
        "targetPattern": "搜番"
      },
      {
        "urlPattern": "host2\\s*=\\s*'([^']+)'",
        "urlDecoding": "none"
      }
    ]
  },
  "capabilities": {
    "requiresHumanVerification": false
  },
  "headers": {
    "User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36",
    "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8"
  },
  "search": {
    "_comment": "占位搜索配置。发布页多跳最终可得到 to.sofan1.cc，但搜索结果正文仍由 iframe 加载，不会在壳页面直接返回；需要拿到稳定直出的 HTML/API 后再补 itemPattern。",
    "method": "GET",
    "url": "/?word={query}",
    "responseType": "html",
    "itemPattern": "",
    "pageSize": 20
  },
  "fields": {
    "sourceItemId": "sourceItemId",
    "title": "title",
    "infoHash": "infoHash",
    "magnet": "magnet",
    "humanSize": "humanSize",
    "seeders": "seeders",
    "webUrl": "webUrl"
  },
  "fileFields": {},
  "defaults": {
    "magnet": "magnet:?xt=urn:btih:{infoHashUpper}",
    "webUrl": "{sourceItemId}"
  }
}
